data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! An outstanding home located in the highly sought-after Magnolia Park Gated Community! Featuring a lovely POOL HOME with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2 -car garage, this home is sure to impress. The open layout with faux stone vinyl flooring guides you to the combined living and dining area, complete with ample space for dining. The kitchen overlooks the family room, making it ideal for both entertaining and everyday relaxation. Step outside to enjoy a fantastic screened inground pool equipped with an Aquacal Pool Heater and Cooler for year-round comfort. Per seller, extra home features of $30,000+!!! The pool features new deck resurfacing, Automated Zodiac MX6 Pool Cleaner, Salt Water Chlorinator, Pentair Intel Automated control panel, and comes with a Fastlane Swim Spa System that lets you swim, exercise, play, and entertain; it’s the perfect fun-and-fitness solution. It also includes FRESHLY PAINTED EXTERIOR, newly installed Culligan House Water Softener System, a safe step walk-in jacuzzi bath tub, fans in all rooms (remote controlled ceiling fans in the living room, dining area, and one bedroom), new gutters, and hurricane shutters to safeguard your home during storms. Take advantage of the Magnolia Park community's numerous amenities, including three pools, basketball courts, walking and biking paths, multiple playgrounds, and much more. Monthly HOA fee includes lawn maintenance; cutting, trimming & mulching offering a hassle-free living! Few minutes away from various dining options, shopping, and close to the Interstate for easy commuting. Also, just a short drive to beaches, MacDill, downtown Tampa, and all the attractions of the vibrant Tampa Bay area. NOT your Average home, LOTS of EXTRA FEATURES!  Don't miss your chance to view this exceptional property!
